title: Google\Cloud\Dlp\V2\CryptoReplaceFfxFpeConfig\FfxCommonNativeAlphabet
name: FfxCommonNativeAlphabet
description:
These are commonly used subsets of the alphabet that the FFX mode natively supports. In the algorithm, the alphabet is selected using the "radix". Therefore each corresponds to particular radix.

Protobuf type google.privacy.dlp.v2.CryptoReplaceFfxFpeConfig.FfxCommonNativeAlphabet
